<br>
I have had 6 pregnancies, and 4 babies, and my pregnancies are all high risk, so with the last baby, we snipped DH, so that we don't have to think about it anymore.<br>
<br>
If health wasn't a consideration, I think, like Gaia, I would have babies forever ;-)<br>
<br>
